      "text": "sum_nums(n):\n    L = n.len\n    for i in 0..L:\n        for j in i+1..L:\n                s = n[i] + n[j]",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "sum_nums(n):\n    L = n.len\n    for i in 0..L:\n        for j in i+1..L:\n                s = n[i] + n[j]",
